@page "/returns-refunds"

<PageTitle>Returns & Refunds — @Tenant.StoreName</PageTitle>

<div class="legal-page">

    <h1>Returns &amp; Refunds</h1>
    <span class="legal-updated">Last updated: January 2025</span>

    <div class="legal-highlight">
        <p>Your satisfaction is our priority. If you are not happy with your purchase, we are here to help. Please read the policy below carefully before requesting a return.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>1. Return Window</h2>
    <p>You may request a return within <strong>14 days</strong> of receiving your order. After this period, we are unable to accept returns unless the item is defective or damaged on arrival.</p>

    <h2>2. Eligibility</h2>
    <p>To be eligible for a return, the item must be:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Unused and in its original condition</li>
        <li>In the original, undamaged packaging</li>
        <li>Accompanied by the order number or proof of purchase</li>
    </ul>
    <p>For hygiene reasons, the following items are <strong>non-returnable</strong> once opened:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Lip products (lipsticks, glosses, lip liners)</li>
        <li>Mascaras and liquid eyeliners</li>
        <li>Foundation, BB cream, and skin-contact products</li>
        <li>Any item marked as final sale</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Damaged or Incorrect Items</h2>
    <p>If your order arrives damaged or you received the wrong item, please contact us within <strong>48 hours</strong> of delivery. We will arrange a replacement or full refund at no cost to you. Please keep the original packaging and take photos if possible.</p>

    <h2>4. How to Request a Return</h2>
    <p>To start a return, contact us by phone at <a href="tel:@Tenant.ContactPhone">@Tenant.ContactPhoneDisplay</a> with your order number and reason for return. We will guide you through the next steps.</p>
    <p>Do not send items back without contacting us first — unannounced returns cannot be processed.</p>

    <h2>5. Refund Process</h2>
    <p>Once we receive and inspect the returned item, we will notify you of the outcome. Approved refunds are processed within <strong>5–7 business days</strong> using the original payment method:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Cash on delivery orders</strong> — refunded via bank transfer or store credit</li>
        <li><strong>Card payments</strong> — refunded to the original card</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Original shipping fees are non-refundable unless the return is due to our error.</p>

    <h2>6. Exchanges</h2>
    <p>We offer exchanges for the same product in a different shade or variant, subject to availability. Contact us and we will do our best to accommodate your request.</p>

    <h2>7. Shipping Costs for Returns</h2>
    <p>Return shipping costs are the responsibility of the customer unless the return is due to a defective or incorrect item, in which case we will cover the cost.</p>

    <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>Have questions? Reach us at <a href="tel:@Tenant.ContactPhone">@Tenant.ContactPhoneDisplay</a>. We aim to respond to all inquiries within 1 business day.</p>

</div>
